    <name>Collective Agency in Action</name>
    <intro></intro>
    <introformat>1</introformat>
    <content>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{3085b80e-f55b-45b9-be45-74a2272705cd}{171}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:0}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Trust is key for creating the conditions within which collective agency can emerge among adult&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;learners. Group action projects and adult learners teaching one another across programs are&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;practices that have a particularly important impact in fostering learners’ collective agency&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="$@PAGEVIEWBYID*9888@$" target="_blank"&gt;(&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="$@PAGEVIEWBYID*9888@$" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Chuang,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;2021)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{3085b80e-f55b-45b9-be45-74a2272705cd}{174}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.15,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:0}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;An example of an action project is the creation of posters on health literacy topics&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;that can be shared&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;with learners across the program so that their efforts have an impact beyond an individual course.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Combined with efforts to build trust through social presence in online courses, the use of action&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;projects and other strategies that build collective agency can result in online learning environments&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;that better motivate adult learners and help them persist in their learning&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;a href="$@PAGEVIEWBYID*9888@$" target="_blank"&gt;(Walter, 2019)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{3085b80e-f55b-45b9-be45-74a2272705cd}{174}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.15,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:0}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{3085b80e-f55b-45b9-be45-74a2272705cd}{177}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:0}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/Try%20It%20Yourself.png" alt="" width="68" height="66" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_middle"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Try it yourself:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;&lt;a href="$@PAGEVIEWBYID*9894@$" target="_blank"&gt;Share this quote with your class and engage in a class discussion&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/Divider%20Wave%20%281%29.png" alt="" width="1920" height="195" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_text-bottom"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
